   "source": [
    "# Session 2: Git Standards & AI-Enhanced Code Reviews\n",
    "\n",
    "> Enforce Conventional Commits, Enterprise Gitflow, and automate PR quality with AI agents."
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "id": "6cf4ceba",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## 1. Conventional Commits Standard"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "id": "e94d402a",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "Format: `<type>(<scope>): <description>`\n",
    "\n",
    "| Type | Purpose |\n",
    "|------|---------|\n",
    "| `feat` | New feature |\n",
    "| `fix` | Bug fix |\n",
    "| `refactor` | Code restructure |\n",
    "| `security` | Security patch |\n",
    "| `test` | Add/update tests |\n",
    "| `chore` | Config, deps |"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "id": "64d619a9",
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "good = [\n",
    "    'feat(auth): implement JWT refresh token rotation',\n",
    "    'fix(payment): handle null card expiry gracefully',\n",
    "    'security(api): sanitize user input on search endpoint',\n",
    "    'refactor(user): extract validation to dedicated service',\n",
    "]\n",
    "bad = ['fix bug', 'update', 'wip', 'asdfgh', 'FINAL_v2']\n",
    "print('✅ GOOD commits:')\n",
    "for c in good: print(f'  {c}')\n",
    "print('\\n❌ BAD commits (will be rejected):')\n",
    "for c in bad: print(f'  {c}')"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "id": "3eea053f",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## 2. Enterprise Gitflow"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "id": "8524a581",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "```\n",
    "main ←── release ←── develop ←── feature/TICKET-ID-description\n",
    "                              ←── hotfix/TICKET-ID-description\n",
    "```\n",
    "**Rules:**\n",
    "- `main`: merge from release/hotfix only, always deployable\n",
    "- `develop`: integration branch, CI must pass\n",
    "- Feature branches: named `feature/PROJ-123-add-oauth`\n",
    "- PRs require: 1 approval + all checks green + no unresolved comments"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "id": "d7c60f6e",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
